* Continuous\nTriggers
** Behavior
***_ Starts new run after previous ends
***_ Runs even after failure
***_ Perpetual execution cycle
** Use Cases
***_ Streaming data processing
***_ Monitoring systems
***_ High-volume ETL
** Cost Consideration
***_ Continuously consumes compute
***_ Use serverless to optimize
** Lifecycle
***_ Resume: waits for active run to end
***_ Pause: stops new runs
@endmindmap
